      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.nk3oUdU4wHeRTn76]{Hive Mind}</p><p>You are in constant telepathic communication with all creatures linked to and within 60 feet of you. If one of you is aware of something, all of you are.<br />When any linked creature wants to spend Resolve Points but doesn&rsquo;t have enough to spend on the desired effect, another linked creature can spend 1 Resolve Point. A creature that does so can then spend its remaining Resolve Points on behalf of the linked creature in need of extra Resolve Points. Once a linked creature spends or receives Resolve Points from this ability, it can&rsquo;t use or benefit from this ability again until after it rests for 8 hours to regain Resolve Points.<br />In addition, creatures linked to you through your hive link connection powers and through your telepathic bond class feature are viable targets for any&nbsp;<em>telepathic jaunt</em> spell you cast.</p>"
